Package alluxio.client

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    BoundedStream
    This interface should be implemented by all Alluxio streams which are bounded at a certain byte size.
    Cancelable
    This interface should be implemented by all Alluxio output streams which support aborting the temporary data that has been written.
    RemoteBlockReader
    The interface to read remote block from data server.
    RemoteBlockWriter
    The interface to write a remote block to the data server.
    Seekable
    This interface should be implemented by all Alluxio streams which support moving the read position to a specific byte offset.
    UnderFileSystemFileReader
    The interface to read an under file system file through a worker's data server.
    UnderFileSystemFileWriter
    The interface to write an under file system file through a worker's data server.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractOutStream
    An abstraction of the output stream API in Alluxio to write data to a file or a block.
    ClientContext
    A shared context in each client JVM.
    FileSystemTestUtils
    Utility class for testing the Alluxio file system.
    RemoteBlockReader.Factory
    The factory for the RemoteBlockReader.
    RemoteBlockWriter.Factory
    The factory for the RemoteBlockWriter.
    UnderFileSystemFileReader.Factory
    The factory for the UnderFileSystemFileReader.
    UnderFileSystemFileWriter.Factory
    The factory for the UnderFileSystemFileWriter.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    AlluxioStorageType
    Specifies the type of data interaction with Alluxio.
    ReadType
    Convenience modes for commonly used read types.
    UnderStorageType
    Specifies the type of data interaction with Alluxio's Under Storage.
    WriteType
    Write types for creating a file in Alluxio.
